				  Gapertium
			  CLI Front-end for Apertium

Requirements
============
- 1x human to install and use the program (the more, the better).
- 1x computer with Unix (TM) based OS.
- 1x Apertium previously installed in the system.
- ?x translation pairs previously installed.

Installation
============
- chmod +x install.sh
- ./install.sh
- gapertium
